3
00:01:33,720 --> 00:01:34,400
Chunsheng,

4
00:01:35,960 --> 00:01:36,720
I now admit that

5
00:01:37,440 --> 00:01:38,480
I lost to you.

6
00:01:40,280 --> 00:01:41,080
Are we still brothers?

7
00:01:42,600 --> 00:01:43,400
Of course.

8
00:01:43,920 --> 00:01:44,880
Get back to your work!

9
00:01:44,920 --> 00:01:46,640
We're working for your
future mother-in-law.

10
00:01:46,640 --> 00:01:47,560
You're the main force.

11
00:01:50,640 --> 00:01:51,280
Guohua,

12
00:01:52,760 --> 00:01:53,440
thanks.

13
00:01:55,000 --> 00:01:55,720
Big deal.

14
00:01:56,480 --> 00:01:57,160
Add some water.

15
00:02:02,840 --> 00:02:03,920
Have some pear soup.

16
00:02:04,920 --> 00:02:05,920
Dongzi, Hongjun, come on.

17
00:02:05,920 --> 00:02:06,960
Thank you, guys.

18
00:02:07,400 --> 00:02:08,000
Come on.

19
00:02:08,160 --> 00:02:10,070
Take a break and have some pear soup.

20
00:02:21,080 --> 00:02:21,720
Hongling,

21
00:02:22,280 --> 00:02:23,720
didn't Guohua say he could ask

22
00:02:24,520 --> 00:02:27,600
Professor Su to schedule surgery for me?

23
00:02:29,520 --> 00:02:30,440
The doctor said,

24
00:02:30,640 --> 00:02:31,840
given your situation,

25
00:02:32,080 --> 00:02:34,160
we could choose conservative treatment

26
00:02:34,400 --> 00:02:35,720
if you took medicine and
did follow-up checks on time.

27
00:02:39,240 --> 00:02:41,400
Why don't you call Guohua and ask him

28
00:02:41,560 --> 00:02:43,000
to consult with Professor Su?

29
00:02:44,440 --> 00:02:46,040
He's only an acquaintance of mine.

30
00:02:46,040 --> 00:02:47,440
I don't want to bother him.

31
00:02:51,280 --> 00:02:53,280
Do you have a problem with him again?

32
00:02:56,040 --> 00:02:56,640
Mom,

33
00:02:57,600 --> 00:02:58,640
I already have a boyfriend.

34
00:02:59,560 --> 00:03:00,920
Is that Chunsheng?

35
00:03:05,000 --> 00:03:05,920
I hear that

36
00:03:06,160 --> 00:03:08,280
his father is still
under isolated review.

37
00:03:08,480 --> 00:03:10,040
His problem hasn't been clarified yet.

38
00:03:11,200 --> 00:03:13,240
Mom, don't be so snobbish, OK?

39
00:03:15,680 --> 00:03:18,120
How can you say that to your mom?

40
00:03:18,440 --> 00:03:19,440
I'm sad.

41
00:03:20,520 --> 00:03:21,520
Don't you know

42
00:03:21,560 --> 00:03:23,400
what a life we've had over the years?

43
00:03:24,160 --> 00:03:25,840
Do you think it's easy for me
to bring you up?

44
00:03:30,600 --> 00:03:31,640
Sorry, Mom.

45
00:03:31,640 --> 00:03:33,040
I shouldn't have said that to you.

46
00:03:33,240 --> 00:03:33,960
Don't be angry.

47
00:03:35,320 --> 00:03:37,000
Mom only wants the best for you.

48
00:03:37,640 --> 00:03:38,760
You're young

49
00:03:38,760 --> 00:03:40,600
and you only think about love.

50
00:03:40,880 --> 00:03:42,200
When you get married,

51
00:03:42,680 --> 00:03:43,760
you'll know how hard life is.

52
00:03:46,360 --> 00:03:48,040
I know what you mean.

53
00:03:49,040 --> 00:03:50,640
But I can't betray my heart.

54
00:03:54,280 --> 00:03:57,240
Silly girl. Why are you so silly?

55
00:03:58,600 --> 00:03:59,960
He Hongling, a call for you.

56
00:04:02,640 --> 00:04:03,200
OK.

57
00:04:04,960 --> 00:04:06,840
Mom, Chunsheng will be here soon.

58
00:04:07,040 --> 00:04:07,960
Be careful with what you say.

59
00:04:14,960 --> 00:04:15,520
Hello.

60
00:04:16,080 --> 00:04:17,310
Hongling, it's me.

61
00:04:18,800 --> 00:04:20,550
Guohua, what's up?

62
00:04:20,680 --> 00:04:22,560
Are you going to take your mom
out of the hospital?

63
00:04:25,200 --> 00:04:25,720
Yes.

64
00:04:25,720 --> 00:04:28,080
Hongling, I've contacted Professor Su.

65
00:04:28,440 --> 00:04:30,080
He'll schedule the surgery.

66
00:04:31,200 --> 00:04:33,360
Guohua, thanks.

67
00:04:33,640 --> 00:04:34,680
But...

68
00:04:34,680 --> 00:04:35,480
Hongling,

69
00:04:36,000 --> 00:04:37,640
I've made it clear with Chunsheng.

70
00:04:38,080 --> 00:04:39,040
No offense.

71
00:04:39,280 --> 00:04:41,080
I just want to help you as a friend.

72
00:04:42,280 --> 00:04:43,520
To tell the truth,

73
00:04:44,200 --> 00:04:45,720
I know you mean well.

74
00:04:46,400 --> 00:04:48,080
But I just can't accept your help

75
00:04:48,080 --> 00:04:49,000
for granted.

76
00:04:49,000 --> 00:04:49,800
Do you understand?

77
00:04:49,960 --> 00:04:50,960
Don't think too much.

78
00:04:53,480 --> 00:04:54,280
I have to go.

79
00:05:01,820 --> 00:05:04,900
(Unit One)

80
00:05:05,240 --> 00:05:06,040
Guys,

81
00:05:06,040 --> 00:05:06,840
listen to me.

82
00:05:07,480 --> 00:05:09,640
For the sake of our
revolutionary friendship,

83
00:05:09,760 --> 00:05:11,520
I've used up all my meat coupons

84
00:05:11,520 --> 00:05:12,720
to treat you guys.

85
00:05:12,720 --> 00:05:14,320
I have to eat grass from now on.

86
00:05:14,320 --> 00:05:15,040
Really?

87
00:05:15,040 --> 00:05:16,080
Don't laugh. I'm telling you,

88
00:05:16,320 --> 00:05:18,720
I won't stand any of you
acting courtesy today.

89
00:05:18,720 --> 00:05:20,400
- We won't do that.
- Enjoy yourselves.

90
00:05:20,400 --> 00:05:21,640
Cheers.

91
00:05:21,640 --> 00:05:22,360
Thanks for your treat.

92
00:05:22,360 --> 00:05:23,240
Cheers.

93
00:05:23,240 --> 00:05:24,600
We may not get another treat again.

94
00:05:31,560 --> 00:05:31,920
Cheers.

95
00:05:32,080 --> 00:05:33,640
Next, I propose us to

96
00:05:34,040 --> 00:05:35,640
drink to Comrade He Hongling.

97
00:05:35,800 --> 00:05:38,400
Congratulations to Hongling
on her glorious enlistment.

98
00:05:38,400 --> 00:05:39,320
- Cheers.
- Cheers.

99
00:05:39,760 --> 00:05:40,480
- Congratulations.
- Cheers.

100
00:05:40,480 --> 00:05:41,360
- Thanks, guys.
- Congratulations, Hongling.

101
00:05:43,200 --> 00:05:43,840
I'll empty it.

102
00:05:46,680 --> 00:05:47,320
Guys,

103
00:05:48,000 --> 00:05:49,360
I've received my call-up notice, too.

104
00:05:49,760 --> 00:05:52,080
I'll join the military with Hongling
in a few days.

105
00:05:52,920 --> 00:05:55,160
Chunsheng, I didn't keep my promise.

106
00:05:55,600 --> 00:05:56,440
Don't say that.

107
00:05:56,640 --> 00:05:57,720
It's a good thing.

108
00:05:58,480 --> 00:05:59,320
You should do it early.

109
00:06:01,040 --> 00:06:02,480
I thought we would

110
00:06:02,480 --> 00:06:03,640
never be parted.

111
00:06:04,880 --> 00:06:06,160
I don't want to leave you guys,

112
00:06:07,520 --> 00:06:08,200
and you.

113
00:06:10,160 --> 00:06:12,840
A fine man is ambitious.

114
00:06:13,360 --> 00:06:15,040
A good friendship will last.

115
00:06:15,040 --> 00:06:15,640
Yeah!

116
00:06:15,960 --> 00:06:17,080
I propose again

117
00:06:17,320 --> 00:06:18,800
to raise our glasses

118
00:06:19,280 --> 00:06:22,440
and congratulate Guohua and Hongling
on their glorious enlistment.

119
00:06:22,440 --> 00:06:23,560
- Cheers.
- Cheers.

120
00:06:23,960 --> 00:06:24,520
Cheers.

121
00:06:24,880 --> 00:06:26,880
Bottoms up!

122
00:06:27,640 --> 00:06:28,640
You're enlisted.

123
00:06:29,600 --> 00:06:31,600
I'll give you a small gift

124
00:06:33,480 --> 00:06:34,480
as a souvenir.

125
00:06:40,720 --> 00:06:43,840
This pen was left by Chunsheng's mom.

126
00:06:44,520 --> 00:06:46,640
It's an American product
seized on the Northeast battlefield.

127
00:06:46,800 --> 00:06:47,480
Though it's old,

128
00:06:47,760 --> 00:06:48,400
it's handy.

129
00:06:49,760 --> 00:06:51,120
Mr. Xiao, I can't accept it.

130
00:06:51,120 --> 00:06:52,200
It's too precious.

131
00:06:52,200 --> 00:06:53,000
I can't accept it.

132
00:06:53,280 --> 00:06:54,440
During the days when I was ill,

133
00:06:55,160 --> 00:06:55,920
thanks for looking after me.

134
00:06:56,840 --> 00:06:57,680
Take it, child.

135
00:07:00,040 --> 00:07:02,000
Write to Chunsheng more
when you get time.

136
00:07:03,240 --> 00:07:04,440
He's lonely

137
00:07:05,080 --> 00:07:05,760
to be left home alone.

138
00:07:09,360 --> 00:07:11,920
Work hard when you join the military,

139
00:07:12,920 --> 00:07:13,840
Comrade He Hongling.

140
00:07:18,080 --> 00:07:19,360
Yes, sir!

141
00:07:25,220 --> 00:07:27,900
(Beijing Railway Station)

142
00:07:33,880 --> 00:07:36,760
Guohua, do well in the military.

143
00:07:37,240 --> 00:07:38,880
Rest assured. I won't disgrace you.

144
00:07:40,080 --> 00:07:42,080
Chunsheng, join us earlier.

145
00:07:44,440 --> 00:07:46,240
They are not going to leave forever.

146
00:07:46,560 --> 00:07:47,160
Big deal.

147
00:07:48,720 --> 00:07:49,960
She's so indifferent.

148
00:07:50,080 --> 00:07:51,520
She doesn't have
any revolutionary emotions.

149
00:08:01,440 --> 00:08:02,080
Enough.

150
00:08:02,400 --> 00:08:03,160
Don't fuss.

151
00:08:04,560 --> 00:08:06,560
Be good to Hongjun after I leave.

152
00:08:06,560 --> 00:08:07,320
Be gentle with him.

153
00:08:07,320 --> 00:08:08,240
Don't always order him around.

154
00:08:19,840 --> 00:08:20,800
Remember my words.

155
00:08:22,840 --> 00:08:23,520
What words?

156
00:08:24,160 --> 00:08:25,320
You tell me.

157
00:08:26,280 --> 00:08:26,960
Alright.

158
00:08:27,320 --> 00:08:27,840
I remember.

159
00:08:29,600 --> 00:08:30,600
Remember to write to me.

160
00:08:31,560 --> 00:08:32,320
One letter a day.

161
00:08:33,040 --> 00:08:34,240
Don't think of other girls.

162
00:08:36,560 --> 00:08:37,520
Yes. Ma'am.

163
00:08:47,880 --> 00:08:50,920
You'll find the right one eventually.

164
00:08:54,680 --> 00:08:55,280
You, too.

165
00:09:04,200 --> 00:09:05,400
Get on.

166
00:09:05,400 --> 00:09:06,450
Bye.

167
00:09:07,920 --> 00:09:08,600
Write to me.

168
00:09:09,480 --> 00:09:10,520
Take care.

169
00:09:10,680 --> 00:09:11,520
Bye.

170
00:09:13,600 --> 00:09:14,160
Go ahead.

171
00:09:15,400 --> 00:09:16,040
Bye, Chunsheng.

172
00:09:16,770 --> 00:09:17,770
- Take care.
- Write to me when you arrive.

173
00:09:18,680 --> 00:09:20,080
Take care.

174
00:09:24,620 --> 00:09:25,420
OK.

175
00:09:34,920 --> 00:09:36,320
Remember to think of me.

176
00:10:24,980 --> 00:10:27,500
(Hard work is our
intrinsic political quality)

177
00:10:27,500 --> 00:10:28,940
(Be vigilant to defend our country)

178
00:10:28,940 --> 00:10:30,260
(Imperialism and all reactionaries
are paper tigers)

179
00:10:30,260 --> 00:10:31,860
(Our native land must not be infringed
Strive to build a strong navy)

180
00:10:33,640 --> 00:10:35,840
I'll wait for you to join me in the army.

181
00:10:37,640 --> 00:10:38,400
We've got a deal.

182
00:10:38,800 --> 00:10:41,000
Let's make our dreams
come true together.

183
00:10:55,080 --> 00:10:57,400
You gave up the chance of
joining the art troupe to He Hongling

184
00:10:57,400 --> 00:10:58,760
to help them,

185
00:10:59,400 --> 00:11:02,200
not expecting to
separate them by mistake.

186
00:11:06,280 --> 00:11:08,320
He Hongling knew Xiao Chunsheng
hadn't passed the political appraisal,

187
00:11:08,320 --> 00:11:09,520
but she still chose to leave.

188
00:11:09,960 --> 00:11:11,120
Do you know why?

189
00:11:14,920 --> 00:11:16,920
Neither my brother nor Xiao Chunsheng

190
00:11:17,200 --> 00:11:17,920
can influence

191
00:11:17,920 --> 00:11:19,600
her inner desires.

192
00:11:20,120 --> 00:11:21,720
Deep down in her heart,
she loves herself the most.

193
00:11:22,920 --> 00:11:25,440
I was only pessimistic about
her being with my brother before,

194
00:11:26,040 --> 00:11:28,560
but now I'm also pessimistic
about her and Xiao Chunsheng.

195
00:11:29,400 --> 00:11:30,680
With every choice she makes,

196
00:11:30,680 --> 00:11:32,720
she pushes Xiao Chunsheng
further away.

197
00:11:33,400 --> 00:11:34,840
Xiao Chunsheng is clever.

198
00:11:35,400 --> 00:11:36,600
Gradually, he'll understand

199
00:11:37,080 --> 00:11:39,040
he can't give He Hongling
the life she wants.

200
00:11:42,960 --> 00:11:45,520
Xiaomei, I think

201
00:11:45,960 --> 00:11:47,680
you're the same kind of person
as Xiao Chunsheng.

202
00:11:48,680 --> 00:11:49,840
Do you also...

203
00:11:51,080 --> 00:11:52,440
I'll bring you some fruit.

204
00:12:00,880 --> 00:12:01,640
Xiao Chunsheng,

205
00:12:02,400 --> 00:12:03,080
a letter for you.

206
00:12:07,280 --> 00:12:08,800
When I'm writing this letter,

207
00:12:09,320 --> 00:12:11,120
I haven't received
your first letter yet.

208
00:12:12,400 --> 00:12:14,680
Yunnan is really far away from Beijing.

209
00:12:16,080 --> 00:12:18,320
Though the training for new recruits
is tough,

210
00:12:18,600 --> 00:12:21,200
I feel full of vigor every day.

211
00:12:21,360 --> 00:12:22,840
I just don't feel tired.

212
00:12:23,560 --> 00:12:24,560
I'm doing well.

213
00:12:25,120 --> 00:12:25,640
What about you?

214
00:12:26,160 --> 00:12:26,840
How are you doing?

215
00:12:28,000 --> 00:12:28,560
By the way,

216
00:12:28,800 --> 00:12:29,680
last night, I dreamed about us

217
00:12:29,680 --> 00:12:31,200
taking your dad to climb the mountain.

218
00:12:33,280 --> 00:12:34,320
I woke up in the middle of the night

219
00:12:36,280 --> 00:12:37,400
and suddenly, I missed you so much.

220
00:12:55,440 --> 00:12:56,280
Xiaomei.

221
00:12:57,160 --> 00:12:58,680
Mr. Xiao's blood pressure is stable.

222
00:12:58,920 --> 00:13:00,240
And he's recovering well.

223
00:13:02,280 --> 00:13:03,000
Sorry to bother you.

224
00:13:03,520 --> 00:13:04,400
Don't say that.

225
00:13:04,680 --> 00:13:05,760
It's my pleasure.

226
00:13:07,000 --> 00:13:08,240
Sit down.

227
00:13:18,520 --> 00:13:19,960
Have some water.

228
00:13:20,800 --> 00:13:23,160
Chunsheng, have you
read the newspaper recently?

229
00:13:26,280 --> 00:13:27,600
Since the Gang of Four was smashed,

230
00:13:27,720 --> 00:13:29,520
gratifying changes have taken place
in all walks of life.

231
00:13:29,880 --> 00:13:33,000
All industries are thriving like
bamboo shoots after rain.

232
00:13:33,000 --> 00:13:34,520
Society has taken on
an altogether new aspect.

233
00:13:34,600 --> 00:13:35,520
Times have changed.

234
00:13:36,080 --> 00:13:37,320
You should pull yourself together

235
00:13:37,920 --> 00:13:40,240
and be more concerned
about this changing world.

236
00:13:54,000 --> 00:13:56,240
Hongling, I've thought it over.

237
00:13:56,800 --> 00:13:58,960
Young people should go out

238
00:13:59,320 --> 00:14:01,040
to embrace the changing world.

239
00:14:02,920 --> 00:14:04,840
You know I've always regarded

240
00:14:04,840 --> 00:14:06,120
joining the military as my life goal.

241
00:14:06,680 --> 00:14:08,040
Though I can't fulfill the wish now,

242
00:14:08,440 --> 00:14:09,400
I won't give up.

243
00:14:10,280 --> 00:14:12,680
But when I'm waiting,

244
00:14:13,240 --> 00:14:14,640
I shouldn't sit at home.

245
00:14:16,000 --> 00:14:18,240
Maybe I should hunt for a job.

246
00:14:30,560 --> 00:14:32,600
Chunsheng, I agree with you.

247
00:14:33,200 --> 00:14:35,560
I'm looking forward to meeting you
in the military camp,

248
00:14:36,040 --> 00:14:37,720
but I also hope
you have a fulfilling life.

249
00:14:38,320 --> 00:14:40,400
I believe wherever you are,

250
00:14:40,400 --> 00:14:41,640
(Glorious tradition of plain living
and hard struggle) you will shine

251
00:14:41,760 --> 00:14:42,760
and make an achievement.

252
00:14:43,640 --> 00:14:45,240
But don't push yourself too hard.

253
00:14:45,840 --> 00:14:47,560
Today, the leaders came to

254
00:14:47,560 --> 00:14:49,280
pick players for the greeting
performance for the new recruits.

255
00:14:49,840 --> 00:14:51,280
(Develop literary and art activities)
I was trembling with nervousness.

256
00:14:51,280 --> 00:14:51,860
(To consolidate the socialist
ideological and cultural front)

257
00:14:52,360 --> 00:14:54,760
But the result is good.

258
00:15:01,080 --> 00:15:04,480
Chunsheng, it's the magazine
Guohua mailed to you.

259
00:15:04,560 --> 00:15:05,400
And a letter.

260
00:15:06,200 --> 00:15:06,920
Thanks, Mr. Niu.

261
00:15:09,800 --> 00:15:10,320
Bye.

262
00:15:10,440 --> 00:15:10,960
OK.

263
00:15:14,380 --> 00:15:14,940
(Develop economy)

264
00:15:19,880 --> 00:15:20,640
You know,

265
00:15:20,960 --> 00:15:23,480
people who come here
are all our regular customers.

266
00:15:23,720 --> 00:15:25,960
Smile at them more.

267
00:15:27,480 --> 00:15:28,520
You have a bright smile.

268
00:15:29,920 --> 00:15:31,000
This is the candy section.

269
00:15:31,000 --> 00:15:32,320
Later on, you...

270
00:15:32,320 --> 00:15:33,040
You stay here.

271
00:15:33,640 --> 00:15:34,640
Get acquainted with the business.

272
00:15:36,160 --> 00:15:38,760
That's the vegetable
and raw food section.

273
00:15:38,920 --> 00:15:41,040
The vegetables are delivered at 5 a.m.

274
00:15:42,640 --> 00:15:43,440
Look here.

275
00:15:45,080 --> 00:15:46,000
Daily necessities section.

276
00:15:47,960 --> 00:15:48,840
Be careful!

277
00:15:49,480 --> 00:15:50,320
Mr. Liu.

278
00:15:50,320 --> 00:15:51,000
Are you OK?

279
00:15:51,920 --> 00:15:53,520
My back hurts so much.

280
00:15:54,080 --> 00:15:54,520
