567
00:30:16,520 --> 00:30:17,440
Do you understand?

568
00:30:17,440 --> 00:30:18,480
Yes.

569
00:30:20,360 --> 00:30:20,840
Hongling,

570
00:30:22,280 --> 00:30:23,080
come with me.

571
00:30:25,600 --> 00:30:26,880
Why her again?

572
00:30:27,080 --> 00:30:27,760
Yeah.

573
00:30:29,120 --> 00:30:30,200
What does Commander
want her to do?

574
00:30:30,320 --> 00:30:31,840
Why does Commander
always single her out?

575
00:30:32,120 --> 00:30:32,880
Hongling.

576
00:30:33,200 --> 00:30:33,880
Sit.

577
00:30:41,800 --> 00:30:43,440
Hongling, have some water.

578
00:30:44,840 --> 00:30:45,600
Thanks, ma'am.

579
00:30:49,200 --> 00:30:51,040
Are your hands fine?

580
00:30:51,080 --> 00:30:51,800
Yeah.

581
00:30:52,480 --> 00:30:54,600
I've paid close attention to
all of you

582
00:30:54,920 --> 00:30:56,880
since you came here.

583
00:30:57,840 --> 00:31:00,000
You're the most hardworking one
among the new recruits.

584
00:31:00,240 --> 00:31:01,360
So I'm optimistic about you

585
00:31:01,600 --> 00:31:02,480
in this selection.

586
00:31:03,000 --> 00:31:03,720
Thanks, ma'am.

587
00:31:03,920 --> 00:31:05,520
I won't disappoint you.

588
00:31:07,720 --> 00:31:09,720
You have good professional skills.

589
00:31:10,080 --> 00:31:11,160
Though you're young,

590
00:31:11,520 --> 00:31:13,560
you're sober and outstanding.

591
00:31:13,840 --> 00:31:14,680
Keep up the good work.

592
00:31:16,000 --> 00:31:17,680
I promise to live up to your trust.

593
00:31:19,560 --> 00:31:20,800
Prepare well when you get back.

594
00:31:20,920 --> 00:31:22,920
The results will
depend on your performance.

595
00:31:23,240 --> 00:31:25,880
This performance
is just a starting point.

596
00:31:26,840 --> 00:31:27,800
Work harder.

597
00:31:30,760 --> 00:31:31,280
Yes.

598
00:32:48,360 --> 00:32:49,560
(When his sister worked overtime,)

599
00:32:50,240 --> 00:32:52,440
(Xiao Chunsheng stayed at home
alone with his father.)

600
00:32:53,120 --> 00:32:55,360
(He took the responsibility)

601
00:32:55,360 --> 00:32:56,880
(of taking care of his father.)

602
00:33:02,640 --> 00:33:03,480
(Every day after breakfast,)

603
00:33:03,800 --> 00:33:06,240
(he left with Ye Fang and Hongjun.)

604
00:33:06,840 --> 00:33:07,960
(He went to the cooperative)

605
00:33:08,320 --> 00:33:10,280
(while the other two
went to the library.)

606
00:33:10,640 --> 00:33:11,360
(Generally,)

607
00:33:11,800 --> 00:33:13,440
(his life was busy)

608
00:33:13,720 --> 00:33:15,240
(and fulfilling these days.)

609
00:33:18,720 --> 00:33:19,360
Chunsheng.

610
00:33:20,320 --> 00:33:21,120
Xiaohui.

611
00:33:21,800 --> 00:33:22,480
You want to see me?

612
00:33:24,600 --> 00:33:26,400
OK. Wait for me outside.

613
00:33:27,080 --> 00:33:27,600
OK.

614
00:33:30,760 --> 00:33:32,240
Master, may I leave for a minute?

615
00:33:33,040 --> 00:33:33,760
Get back quickly.

616
00:33:38,360 --> 00:33:39,240
I'll be back soon.

617
00:33:44,160 --> 00:33:47,120
Xiaohui, you didn't tell me last time.

618
00:33:48,400 --> 00:33:49,120
Did Heizi

619
00:33:50,120 --> 00:33:51,320
hurt you?

620
00:33:53,760 --> 00:33:54,440
It's OK.

621
00:33:55,040 --> 00:33:55,840
What happened?

622
00:33:56,240 --> 00:33:57,200
Why did he hit you?

623
00:34:00,240 --> 00:34:02,360
I was training with the team that day.

624
00:34:02,360 --> 00:34:03,720
The coach corrected my movements.

625
00:34:04,080 --> 00:34:04,800
You know

626
00:34:05,000 --> 00:34:06,440
physical contact is normal

627
00:34:06,520 --> 00:34:08,520
during instruction.

628
00:34:09,600 --> 00:34:11,710
But he wasn't happy about it.

629
00:34:12,040 --> 00:34:13,320
He took some guys to intercept my coach.

630
00:34:13,710 --> 00:34:14,960
I tried to stop them.

631
00:34:15,120 --> 00:34:18,920
He might have hit me
by mistake in chaos.

632
00:34:19,320 --> 00:34:20,000
It's OK.

633
00:34:20,920 --> 00:34:22,120
Did he do this before?

634
00:34:22,480 --> 00:34:25,160
No, he didn't.

635
00:34:25,600 --> 00:34:27,360
I don't know
what's wrong with him now.

636
00:34:27,710 --> 00:34:29,520
He seems to be very jealous.

637
00:34:31,960 --> 00:34:33,360
With one of his eyes injured,

638
00:34:34,160 --> 00:34:35,190
he doesn't think he's worthy of you.

639
00:34:38,120 --> 00:34:41,880
Actually, I know people's opinions
about me.

640
00:34:42,190 --> 00:34:43,600
I admit I'm a vain woman.

641
00:34:44,040 --> 00:34:45,190
I enjoy the feeling

642
00:34:45,270 --> 00:34:47,120
of being envied by others.

643
00:34:47,750 --> 00:34:48,960
But do you believe me?

644
00:34:49,320 --> 00:34:50,560
I've never done anything

645
00:34:50,560 --> 00:34:52,120
that would hurt Heizi.

646
00:34:52,560 --> 00:34:54,120
And no matter what he becomes,

647
00:34:54,520 --> 00:34:55,670
I won't frown upon him.

648
00:34:56,520 --> 00:34:57,120
I believe you.

649
00:34:59,200 --> 00:34:59,880
Thanks.

650
00:35:02,680 --> 00:35:04,080
He's such a fool.

651
00:35:04,440 --> 00:35:06,120
He is on guard against everyone,

652
00:35:06,240 --> 00:35:07,160
but he doesn't know

653
00:35:07,480 --> 00:35:09,520
the real goat sticks with him every day.

654
00:35:10,000 --> 00:35:10,480
Well,

655
00:35:10,960 --> 00:35:12,000
what do you mean?

656
00:35:12,720 --> 00:35:15,000
Chunsheng, that's what I came for.

657
00:35:15,520 --> 00:35:17,200
That scumbag, Li Shangyou,

658
00:35:17,200 --> 00:35:18,560
is definitely not a good guy.

659
00:35:19,120 --> 00:35:21,320
He holds a grudge against you
for what happened before.

660
00:35:21,320 --> 00:35:22,000
Do you know that?

661
00:35:23,440 --> 00:35:24,360
That's why.

662
00:35:25,560 --> 00:35:27,400
The problem is,

663
00:35:28,360 --> 00:35:29,240
Heizi still

664
00:35:29,600 --> 00:35:32,720
harbors resentment toward
Chen Hongjun for hurting him.

665
00:35:32,720 --> 00:35:33,760
He can't let it off his mind.

666
00:35:34,160 --> 00:35:36,400
And you're Chen Hongjun's protector.

667
00:35:36,520 --> 00:35:37,720
So I'm worried.

668
00:35:37,720 --> 00:35:39,960
I'm worried that if one day, Li Shangyou

669
00:35:39,960 --> 00:35:41,240
instigates Heizi to do

670
00:35:41,400 --> 00:35:42,840
some radical things

671
00:35:42,840 --> 00:35:44,120
to you and Chen Hongjun,

672
00:35:44,600 --> 00:35:46,760
it will not only hurt you guys

673
00:35:47,360 --> 00:35:47,840
but...

674
00:35:49,040 --> 00:35:51,280
but also cause Heizi huge trouble.

675
00:35:52,200 --> 00:35:53,000
So, Chunsheng,

676
00:35:53,320 --> 00:35:55,080
you must be careful.

677
00:35:55,400 --> 00:35:57,880
You must be on guard
against Li Shangyou.

678
00:35:59,160 --> 00:36:00,240
Thanks, Xiaohui.

679
00:36:00,760 --> 00:36:01,320
I get it.

680
00:36:02,440 --> 00:36:03,000
Alright.

681
00:36:03,480 --> 00:36:05,200
I've told you everything I should.

682
00:36:05,520 --> 00:36:06,520
I have to go home.

683
00:36:06,880 --> 00:36:08,560
Heizi doesn't know I'm out.

684
00:36:08,720 --> 00:36:09,280
Xiaohui,

685
00:36:10,240 --> 00:36:12,120
I know you truly love Heizi.

686
00:36:12,360 --> 00:36:13,760
But nothing is

687
00:36:14,280 --> 00:36:15,600
more important than yourself.

688
00:36:15,880 --> 00:36:18,000
If you want to leave him,

689
00:36:18,840 --> 00:36:19,560
I can help you.

690
00:36:20,120 --> 00:36:21,280
No, no, Chunsheng.

691
00:36:22,000 --> 00:36:22,560
Well,

692
00:36:23,280 --> 00:36:25,560
I know what I should do.

693
00:36:26,040 --> 00:36:26,600
Thanks.

694
00:36:27,600 --> 00:36:28,280
Bye.

695
00:36:36,520 --> 00:36:38,440
The other day I passed by
Mrs. Huang's office.

696
00:36:38,480 --> 00:36:40,120
Guess what I overheard?

697
00:36:40,200 --> 00:36:41,600
What? You sound so cryptic.

698
00:36:42,120 --> 00:36:44,520
Mrs. Huang encouraged
He Hongling to sign up.

699
00:36:44,720 --> 00:36:45,240
You know,

700
00:36:45,440 --> 00:36:47,280
we have so many members
with excellent skills.

701
00:36:47,600 --> 00:36:50,080
Why did she single her out
and encourage her?

702
00:36:52,760 --> 00:36:54,880
Mrs. Huang promised
it would be open and fair.

703
00:36:55,200 --> 00:36:57,000
Everyone can sign up.

704
00:36:57,000 --> 00:36:57,920
But only your competence

705
00:36:57,920 --> 00:36:59,440
can determine the result.

706
00:36:59,480 --> 00:37:01,280
If you have time to gossip,

707
00:37:01,520 --> 00:37:02,480
why don't you practice more?

708
00:37:08,000 --> 00:37:08,720
Chunsheng,

709
00:37:09,000 --> 00:37:10,520
the performance is coming soon.

710
00:37:10,920 --> 00:37:13,920
Mrs. Huang said I was her favorite
among the new recruits.

711
00:37:14,000 --> 00:37:15,560
She encouraged me to sign up.

712
00:37:15,880 --> 00:37:18,240
I'll work hard to pass the selection.

713
00:37:20,080 --> 00:37:21,960
What have you been doing recently?

714
00:37:22,240 --> 00:37:22,880
I miss you.

715
00:37:25,760 --> 00:37:27,520
Hongling, I'm fine.

716
00:37:28,320 --> 00:37:29,480
There's great news.

717
00:37:29,960 --> 00:37:31,640
The college entrance examination
is finally resumed.

718
00:37:32,160 --> 00:37:33,960
Ye Fang and Hongjun were so excited
that they cried.

719
00:37:34,560 --> 00:37:35,720
(To He Hongling)
I'm happy for them.

720
00:37:36,000 --> 00:37:38,160
But lately, Guo Heizi is fooling around

721
00:37:38,160 --> 00:37:39,360
with Li Shangyou again.

722
00:37:39,600 --> 00:37:41,120
They want to retaliate against Hongjun.

723
00:37:41,520 --> 00:37:42,440
Don't worry.

724
00:37:42,760 --> 00:37:43,560
In this world,

725
00:37:43,560 --> 00:37:45,240
there's nothing I can't solve.

726
00:37:45,920 --> 00:37:46,880
I'll protect him.

727
00:37:47,800 --> 00:37:48,800
I miss you, too.

728
00:37:50,820 --> 00:37:52,740
(Long live our great Party
Long live the great unity of the world)

729
00:37:59,240 --> 00:38:00,320
I'm going to the canteen

730
00:38:00,520 --> 00:38:01,240
to get some groceries.

731
00:38:01,400 --> 00:38:01,960
Go ahead.

732
00:38:01,960 --> 00:38:02,520
See you later.

733
00:38:02,520 --> 00:38:03,080
OK.

734
00:38:05,360 --> 00:38:06,040
I have to go.

735
00:38:07,240 --> 00:38:07,880
Wait.

736
00:38:09,480 --> 00:38:10,080
What's up?

737
00:38:11,800 --> 00:38:13,160
These days,

738
00:38:13,160 --> 00:38:15,360
you always seem nervous and preoccupied.

739
00:38:15,960 --> 00:38:17,120
Do you have any problems?

740
00:38:18,440 --> 00:38:19,400
No big deal.

741
00:38:19,680 --> 00:38:20,400
Don't worry about it.

742
00:38:20,720 --> 00:38:21,600
Xiao Chunsheng,

743
00:38:22,120 --> 00:38:23,400
do you know what

744
00:38:23,400 --> 00:38:24,040
your biggest problem is?

745
00:38:24,960 --> 00:38:25,640
What is it?

746
00:38:26,320 --> 00:38:27,200
You always like to

747
00:38:27,200 --> 00:38:29,200
carry others' responsibilities
on your own shoulders.

748
00:38:29,200 --> 00:38:31,560
The relationship between you,
my brother, and He Hongling

749
00:38:32,040 --> 00:38:34,080
got tangled because of your concession.

750
00:38:34,280 --> 00:38:35,040
You don't understand

751
00:38:35,040 --> 00:38:36,440
the years of friendship

752
00:38:37,160 --> 00:38:38,160
between Guohua and me.

753
00:38:39,720 --> 00:38:40,640
Will you tell me?

754
00:38:41,840 --> 00:38:43,320
I don't want to say much more

755
00:38:43,760 --> 00:38:44,520
except one thing.

756
00:38:45,320 --> 00:38:46,360
Tell Hongjun

757
00:38:46,800 --> 00:38:47,520
to stay safe.

758
00:38:48,240 --> 00:38:48,880
Gotta go.

759
00:38:51,760 --> 00:38:52,760
By car?

760
00:38:52,840 --> 00:38:53,440
Yeah.

761
00:38:53,840 --> 00:38:55,760
To save more time for studying,

762
00:38:55,960 --> 00:38:57,160
I asked my dad to let us

763
00:38:57,560 --> 00:38:58,680
take his car

764
00:38:58,760 --> 00:39:00,400
to the library from now on.

765
00:39:00,680 --> 00:39:02,600
Is it appropriate?

766
00:39:02,680 --> 00:39:03,840
Why isn't it appropriate?

767
00:39:04,080 --> 00:39:04,680
Let's go.

768
00:39:07,660 --> 00:39:09,380
(Program List of the
New Recruits Performance)

769
00:39:09,400 --> 00:39:11,760
Hongling, you got selected.

770
00:39:12,040 --> 00:39:14,160
In the future, if anyone says again
you are incompetent

771
00:39:14,160 --> 00:39:16,160
and only joined the troupe
through connections,

772
00:39:16,160 --> 00:39:18,400
let's throw the program list
at their face

773
00:39:18,680 --> 00:39:20,000
and shut them up.

774
00:39:20,840 --> 00:39:22,440
I don't care about what they say.

775
00:39:22,440 --> 00:39:23,120
I know well

776
00:39:23,120 --> 00:39:24,320
about my real ability.

777
00:39:24,440 --> 00:39:25,280
No way.

778
00:39:25,480 --> 00:39:27,680
Kind people are always bullied.

779
00:39:27,840 --> 00:39:29,800
You should be tough sometimes.

780
00:39:30,400 --> 00:39:31,400
Sure. Sure.

781
00:39:31,400 --> 00:39:32,160
I get it.

782
00:39:41,120 --> 00:39:41,560
Chunsheng.

783
00:39:48,160 --> 00:39:48,600
Chunsheng.

784
00:39:49,240 --> 00:39:51,120
Chunsheng, they're here for you.

785
00:39:54,200 --> 00:39:54,840
Heizi,

786
00:39:54,840 --> 00:39:56,960
they have nothing to do with this.

787
00:39:57,440 --> 00:39:59,760
Let's talk outside, OK?

788
00:40:00,160 --> 00:40:01,160
I won't go anywhere.

789
00:40:01,600 --> 00:40:02,600
Let's talk here.

790
00:40:04,920 --> 00:40:06,560
OK. Go ahead.

791
00:40:07,080 --> 00:40:08,160
Did Xiaohui

792
00:40:09,400 --> 00:40:10,840
come to see you?

793
00:40:14,520 --> 00:40:15,200
Xiao Chunsheng,

794
00:40:15,200 --> 00:40:18,000
a leopard can't change its spots.

795
00:40:18,240 --> 00:40:19,600
First, it was He Hongling.

796
00:40:19,840 --> 00:40:21,240
Now, it's Xiaohui.

797
00:40:21,480 --> 00:40:22,400
What do you want?

798
00:40:22,560 --> 00:40:24,720
You can't stop coveting
your brothers' women.

799
00:40:24,720 --> 00:40:26,080
Is that some kind of habit?

800
00:40:26,080 --> 00:40:26,760
Heizi,

801
00:40:27,200 --> 00:40:28,760
watch your mouth.

802
00:40:29,400 --> 00:40:31,920
Yeah, Xiaohui came to see me.

803
00:40:32,160 --> 00:40:33,600
But she was worried about you.

804
00:40:33,840 --> 00:40:34,880
About me?

805
00:40:35,040 --> 00:40:35,640
Yeah.

806
00:40:36,200 --> 00:40:37,400
She was worried about you.

807
00:40:37,680 --> 00:40:39,040
She asked me to persuade you.

808
00:40:42,480 --> 00:40:43,000
Heizi,

809
00:40:44,200 --> 00:40:46,080
there's no free lunch in the world,

810
00:40:46,240 --> 00:40:49,240
let alone ask a tiger for its skin.

811
00:40:51,040 --> 00:40:54,080
Some people bow down to you

812
00:40:54,080 --> 00:40:55,240
and cotton up to you

813
00:40:55,240 --> 00:40:56,760
only forced by the situation.

814
00:40:56,760 --> 00:40:58,120
If one day they get the upper hand,

815
00:40:58,680 --> 00:41:00,520
they'll pay you back all the shit

816
00:41:00,640 --> 00:41:01,760
they have taken from you.

817
00:41:02,000 --> 00:41:03,120
Heizi, listen to me.

818
00:41:03,120 --> 00:41:05,320
Don't be blinded by short-term benefits.

819
00:41:05,920 --> 00:41:07,760
People who would do anything
for benefits

820
00:41:08,400 --> 00:41:09,520
aren't your brothers.

821
00:41:13,480 --> 00:41:16,400
Xiao Chunsheng, are you hinting at me?

822
00:41:25,480 --> 00:41:26,840
I find that

823
00:41:26,920 --> 00:41:28,400
you're good at fomenting dissension.

824
00:41:28,760 --> 00:41:30,480
People like me are not brothers,

825
00:41:30,480 --> 00:41:31,400
but you are.

826
00:41:32,120 --> 00:41:33,480
I hear that He Hongling

827
00:41:34,000 --> 00:41:35,520
is your girlfriend now.

828
00:41:36,160 --> 00:41:38,080
Wasn't she Qi Tian's girlfriend?

829
00:41:40,880 --> 00:41:42,000
I also heard that

830
00:41:42,600 --> 00:41:44,760
she had a past with your good brother,

831
00:41:44,880 --> 00:41:45,760
Ye Guohua.

832
00:41:48,000 --> 00:41:49,640
Is that the brotherhood

833
00:41:50,640 --> 00:41:52,720
you always boast about?

834
00:41:52,720 --> 00:41:53,960
Li Shangyou, I'm telling you.

835
00:41:54,680 --> 00:41:56,040
I don't have the obligation

836
00:41:56,040 --> 00:41:57,240
to explain to you what happened

837
00:41:57,240 --> 00:41:58,400
between Qi Tian, He Hongling,

838
00:41:58,760 --> 00:41:59,960
Ye Guohua, and me!

839
00:42:00,920 --> 00:42:01,760
But,

840
00:42:02,000 --> 00:42:02,960
He Hongling has never done

841
00:42:02,960 --> 00:42:04,320
anything wrong to Tian.

842
00:42:06,480 --> 00:42:07,600
I know that.

843
00:42:08,240 --> 00:42:11,040
Tian entrusted He Hongling to you

844
00:42:11,040 --> 00:42:12,000
and asked you to take care of her.

845
00:42:12,440 --> 00:42:13,240
Not only Hongling,

846
00:42:14,040 --> 00:42:15,440
he entrusted

847
00:42:15,560 --> 00:42:17,200
all of us to you.

848
00:42:18,440 --> 00:42:19,960
I just don't understand.

849
00:42:21,240 --> 00:42:24,000
Why are you guys

850
00:42:24,840 --> 00:42:27,080
so self-righteous?

